# BANG MEMORY DELTA — SESSION 20260424 LATE
## DELTA SUMMARY
Session nay la session **runtime_owner** dau tien cho Bang (per scope delegation session 20260424).
Shipped: 5 commits (P5 + K1 scaffold + K3 v1.0 + K3 v1.1 + SPEC_RADIATION).
## §1. VACCIN UPGRADES (5 levels)
Session demonstrate **evolutionary learning** qua 5 vaccin versions trong 1 session:
### §1.1 Vaccin v1 (sau SCAR-FILENAME-VERIFY P5)
Sau cp file moi:
  ls -la <full-path>  # verify size + name match truoc khi add
### §1.2 Vaccin v2 (sau SCAR-PATH-VERIFY K1)
Sau cp:
  1. ls -la <full-path>
  2. find -name <filename> | expect 1 result only
### §1.3 Vaccin v3 (sau SCAR-PATH-PARADIGM K3 fail 1)
Truoc khi chon path:
  1. Doc SPEC chu quan folder (neu co)
  2. Tranh confuse: spec/ vs result/ vs memory/ vs runtime/
  3. Audit doc tay → audit/reports/ (NOT runtime/audit/)
### §1.4 Vaccin v4 (sau SCAR-IGNORE-BLOCK K3 fail 2)
Workflow git add FULL:
  1. ls -la <path>            (file ton tai)
  2. find <filename>           (no duplicate)
  3. git check-ignore -v       (exit 1 = OK, exit 0 = ABORT)
  4. head -5 <path>            (header correct)
  5. git add <path>            (add CHI file nay, khong wildcard)
### §1.5 Vaccin v5 (sau SCAR-missing-CROSS-DOMAIN-LINK)
Khi blocker nhan thuc (not technical):
  1. Hoi Gatekeeper keyword theo CONCEPT (khong phai task name)
  2. Scan bang.zip voi keyword
  3. CROSS-LINK hits tu nhieu file khac nhau
  4. Derive missing piece TRUOC KHI quay lai implement
